<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Marketing Digital y Diseño Web con IA - Tu Aliado en Málaga</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Agencia especializada en marketing digital y diseño web con inteligencia artificial. Trabajamos con autónomos y PYMEs para potenciar su negocio online.">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #F9FAFB;
      color: #111827;
    }
    .bg-primary {
      background-color: #4F46E5;
    }
    .text-primary {
      color: #4F46E5;
    }
    .text-secondary {
      color: #10B981;
    }
    .hover-bg {
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .hover\:text-gray-900:hover {
      color: #4F46E5;
    }
    .hover\:bg-indigo-500:hover {
      background-color: #3730A3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="bg-white">
    <header class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 z-50">
      <nav class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 lg:px-8" aria-label="Global">
        <!-- Logo -->
        <div class="flex lg:flex-1">
          <a href="/" class="-m-1.5 p-1.5">
            <span class="sr-only">Empresa de Marketing Digital</span>
            <img class="h-8 w-auto" src="https://tailwindui.com/plus/img/logos/mark.svg?color=indigo&shade=600" alt="Logotipo de la empresa" loading="lazy">
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Menú de móvil -->
        <div class="flex lg:hidden">
          <button type="button" class="-m-2.5 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md p-2.5 text-gray-700">
            <span class="sr-only">Abrir menú</span>
            <svg class="size-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 6.75h16.5M3.75 12h16.5m-16.5 5.25h16.5" />
            </svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Menú Desktop -->
        <div class="hidden lg:flex lg:gap-x-12">
          <a href="#inicio" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-primary">Inicio</a>
          <a href="#sobrenosotros" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-primary">Sobre nosotros</a>
          <a href="#carousel" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-primary">Características</a>
          <a href="#preguntas" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-primary">Preguntas frecuentes</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Botón Log in -->
        <div class="hidden lg:flex lg:flex-1 lg:justify-end">
          <a href="#login" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-primary">Log in <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <!-- Mobile menu -->
      <div class="lg:hidden" role="dialog" aria-modal="true">
        <div class="fixed inset-0 z-50"></div>
        <div class="fixed inset-y-0 right-0 z-50 w-full overflow-y-auto bg-white px-6 py-6 sm:max-w-sm sm:ring-1 sm:ring-gray-900/10">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <a href="/" class="-m-1.5 p-1.5">
              <span class="sr-only">Empresa de Marketing Digital</span>
              <img class="h-8 w-auto" src="https://tailwindui.com/plus/img/logos/mark.svg?color=indigo&shade=600" alt="Logotipo de la empresa" loading="lazy">
            </a>
            <button type="button" class="-m-2.5 rounded-md p-2.5 text-gray-700">
              <span class="sr-only">Cerrar menú</span>
              <svg class="size-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flow-root">
            <div class="-my-6 divide-y divide-gray-500/10">
              <div class="space-y-2 py-6">
                <a href="#inicio" class="-mx-3 block rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">Inicio</a>
                <a href="#sobrenosotros" class="-mx-3 block rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">Sobre nosotros</a>
                <a href="#carousel" class="-mx-3 block rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">Características</a>
                <a href="#preguntas" class="-mx-3 block rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">Preguntas frecuentes</a>
              </div>
              <div class="py-6">
                <a href="#login" class="-mx-3 block rounded-lg px-3 py-2.5 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-50">Log in</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="relative isolate px-6 pt-14 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl py-32 sm:py-48 lg:py-56 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-7xl">Datos para potenciar tu negocio online</h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-lg font-medium text-gray-500 sm:text-xl">Usamos tecnología de marketing digital y diseño web con IA para llevar tu negocio al siguiente nivel.</p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
          <a href="#contacto" class="rounded-md bg-primary px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-xs hover:bg-indigo-500">¡Contáctanos!</a>
          <a href="#servicios" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 hover:text-primary">Más información <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
